# ── Frontend environment variables ────────────────────────
#
# USAGE:
#   Dev:  copy to .env.local — Vite loads it automatically, never commit it
#   Prod: set these as CI/CD environment variables (GitHub Actions secrets)
#         they are injected at `npm run build` time, not at runtime
#
# Vite only exposes variables prefixed with VITE_ to the browser.
# Never put secrets here — these values are visible in the built JS bundle.

# ── API ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# URL of the FastAPI backend.
# Dev:  leave empty — Vite proxy handles routing to http://api:8000
# Prod: https://api.yourdomain.com
VITE_API_URL=

# ── Grafana ────────────────────────────────────────────────
# URL of the Grafana dashboard shown in the App System Dashboard section.
# Dev:  leave empty — MetricsPanel falls back to http://<hostname>:3001
# Prod: https://grafana.yourdomain.com
VITE_GRAFANA_URL=
